OL,3,C'Corridor care crisis' - Nurse lifts
OL,4,Clid on hospital frontline services
OL,6,FA nurse from Gloucestershire has
OL,7,Flifted the lid on the shocking reality
OL,8,Fof 'corridor care' in NHS hospitals.
OL,10,FNurse Matthew Stewart said he has had
OL,11,Fto change and toilet some patients
OL,12,Fwaiting in a corridor behind a
OL,13,F"makeshift screen".
OL,15,FHis account comes after a damning
OL,16,Freport was published by the Royal
OL,17,FCollege of Nursing detailing the
OL,18,Fextent of the UK's 'corridor care
OL,19,Fcrisis'.
