OL,3,C'Corridor care crisis' - Nurse lifts
OL,4,Clid on hospital frontline services
OL,6,FHundreds of nurses were asked to share
OL,7,Ftheir experiences of frontline care,
OL,8,Fwith many critical of current NHS
OL,9,Fconditions.
OL,11,FMatthew said: "Some of the stuff I've
OL,12,Fheard is around people acutely
OL,13,Fdeteriorating in these areas
OL,14,F(corridors) and not having access to
OL,15,Fequipment or limited space.
OL,17,F"It's the moral injury and moral
OL,18,Fdistress that it's causing nursing
OL,19,Fstaff and obviously also patient harm,
OL,20,Fas well."
