OL,3,C'Corridor care crisis' - Nurse lifts
OL,4,Clid on hospital frontline services
OL,6,FLast week was the busiest yet for the
OL,7,Fhealth service this winter, with
OL,8,Fhospitals across the UK at almost full
OL,9,Fcapacity.
OL,11,FData from NHS England shows more
OL,12,Fhospital beds were occupied last week
OL,13,Fthan at any point so far this winter
OL,14,F(97,636), with 96% of adult general
OL,15,Fand acute hospital beds having
OL,16,Fpatients in them.
